result.name: The Italian Club Wine Bar, Steak House & Pizza Gourmet

html_attributions: The Italian Club Wine Bar, Steak House & Pizza Gourmet

reviews.text: Nice staff. Good food. Comfort place. Its food for celebrate b day here. I love the pasta and feeling sweet when serving the welcome drinks

For those who like real Italian food taste!
Once you have found it, have have reserved your seat (only about 30 available) you can chose your wine within an incredible list with a Italy 360d origins.
Pizza is only one to choose but beef and all other traditional dishes will be welcomed by your palate.. a place to be for a real dinner experience

The food here is fine. I like the pizza more, the parma ham was well handled so it’s not salty at all, even thought it’s been aged for 20 years (well, according to the menu). But for the black truffle spaghetti, it’s just fine. The amount of truffle put wasn’t not enough, only 2-3pieces. Also, the noodles weren’t chewy enough. And lastly, the dish was served warm only so you will have to finish it within a short time or it will go cold quickly...
The music was good and it’s cozy in there but downside is that table is too small. We ordered a side, pizza, spaghetti and two drinks and we didn’t have enough space for them when they all came at the same time. We had to move carefully because of that...

Attentive service. Nice surprise complimentary welcome drink. Fast service. Didn’t like the extremely cramped seating arrangement and sharing of our tables like in a dai pai dong. Food portions small so not price worthy.

Got their mail about their newly launched all day bfast.   Gave a try.   Got 5-6 choices,  including 1 for veggie.   Ordered an eggs and more@hk$48.  Good taste at good price.   The place is cozy.   No people rushing in and out.   You can relax and spend an hour for your bfast without pressure.   They are offering buy 1 get 1 free for all day bfast til 14 Aug 2019.

reviews.text: Nice staff. Good food. Comfort place. Its food for celebrate b day here. I love the pasta and feeling sweet when serving the welcome drinks

For those who like real Italian food taste!
Once you have found it, have have reserved your seat (only about 30 available) you can chose your wine within an incredible list with a Italy 360d origins.
Pizza is only one to choose but beef and all other traditional dishes will be welcomed by your palate.. a place to be for a real dinner experience

The food here is fine. I like the pizza more, the parma ham was well handled so it’s not salty at all, even thought it’s been aged for 20 years (well, according to the menu). But for the black truffle spaghetti, it’s just fine. The amount of truffle put wasn’t not enough, only 2-3pieces. Also, the noodles weren’t chewy enough. And lastly, the dish was served warm only so you will have to finish it within a short time or it will go cold quickly...
The music was good and it’s cozy in there but downside is that table is too small. We ordered a side, pizza, spaghetti and two drinks and we didn’t have enough space for them when they all came at the same time. We had to move carefully because of that...

上菜速度非常慢 (等了25分鐘），是外國人的style。 牛扒我們是odder medium的， 但是熟了一點，而且肉質普通，味道都還算好吃。 pizza 的包皮不錯，但是芝士份量不足，令味道普通，但熱哄哄的上菜，令整個感覺有所提升。他們的white house wine (Chardonnay)很難喝。 
如果只是這種質素的食物來說，有一點貴，平均二百元一個人，但環境很舒服， 比起來這裏吃午餐，更加適合喝酒聊天， 雖然他們的house wine不太好，但以吧檯的規模來看， 他們應該還算熟悉酒類， 有機會可以試試，但是食物真的不敢恭維。
叫外賣的話，要考慮清楚。卡邦尼粗管意粉，收成$160＋，得細個A5大小的外賣盒的3分2，都唔夠。汁得2湯匙咁多。變得乾而無味。超級搵笨。
